    <item>
      <title>拜登解冻后习近平采取一系列小步骤开放中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/xi-takes-flurry-of-small-steps-to-open-china-after-biden-thaw</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平主席领导的政府誓言要在这一年里恢复外国投资者对中国破碎的信心。自从与美国领导人乔·拜登的会晤稳定了两国关系以来，北京正在逐步将其承诺付诸行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/xi-takes-flurry-of-small-steps-to-open-china-after-biden-thaw</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 02:50:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统在投票前任命新的政策职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/south-korea-president-forms-new-post-for-policy-ahead-of-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈设立了一个新的政策职位，并更换了所有五名高级秘书，就在几个月前举行的选举中，他的政党正试图重新获得议会的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/south-korea-president-forms-new-post-for-policy-ahead-of-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 01:05:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
