    <item>
      <title>特朗普将跳过阿拉巴马州的共和党辩论以举办筹款活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/trump-will-skip-republican-debate-in-alabama-to-host-fundraiser</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普将缺席下周的共和党总统辩论，前往佛罗里达州哈伦代尔海滩参加竞选筹款活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/trump-will-skip-republican-debate-in-alabama-to-host-fundraiser</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 22:39:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克承诺投入 16 亿英镑，试图向 COP28 传达他的信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/sunak-pledges-1-6-billion-to-try-to-show-cop28-he-s-on-message</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 将承诺在气候项目上投入 16 亿英镑（20 亿美元），这位英国首相抵达 COP28 峰会，试图向领导人表明，在他淡化政府的绿色议程并承诺提振石油产量后，英国仍然致力于这一事业和天然气勘探。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/sunak-pledges-1-6-billion-to-try-to-show-cop28-he-s-on-message</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和印度淡化锡克教谋杀阴谋，大亚洲战略面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/us-india-play-down-murder-plot-with-wider-asia-strategy-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有关印度政府特工下令在纽约杀害一名美国公民的指控可能会破坏拜登政府加深与总理纳伦德拉·莫迪政府关系的努力，尽管双方目前都在淡化这一事件的重要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/us-india-play-down-murder-plot-with-wider-asia-strategy-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称以色列不得重蹈加沙北部破坏的覆辙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/us-says-israel-must-not-repeat-scale-of-north-gaza-destruction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯表示，他告诉以色列领导人，他们在准备向南推进军事行动以铲除哈马斯之际，绝不能重蹈加沙地带北部遭受的大规模破坏和流离失所的覆辙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/us-says-israel-must-not-repeat-scale-of-north-gaza-destruction</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 20:15:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共同社称香港记者北京之行后失踪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/south-china-morning-post-reporter-missing-after-beijing-trip-kyodo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据共同社周四报道，自 10 月份前往北京报道防务论坛以来，香港主要英文报纸的一名记者一直无法联系上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/south-china-morning-post-reporter-missing-after-beijing-trip-kyodo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:43:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度出口民调显示莫迪将在激烈的竞选中赢得关键州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/india-exit-polls-predict-tough-fight-for-modi-in-state-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[出口民意调查显示，总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度人民党在两项关键州选举中均领先反对党，这让他在明年的全国投票之前获得了支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/india-exit-polls-predict-tough-fight-for-modi-in-state-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:15:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国缅怀基辛格为中美关系中的“重要老朋友”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/china-remembers-kissinger-as-valued-old-friend-in-us-relations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国向帮助这个亚洲国家向西方开放的美国前国务卿亨利·基辛格表示敬意，称他对建立两个经济超级大国之间的关系具有不可估量的作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/china-remembers-kissinger-as-valued-old-friend-in-us-relations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 05:19:48 GMT</pubDate>
